  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" data-style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; font-size: 16px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0em;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;widows: 1;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n    <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;visibility: visible;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">大模型智能｜分享</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;visibility: visible;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 11px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">来源 | 机器学习算法那些事</span></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">专家混合（MoE）是一种流行的架构，比如最近火爆天的 DeepSeek V3 和 R1 就是这类模型。它利用不同的“专家”来改进 Transformer 模型。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面的示意图展示了它们与 Transformer 的不同之处。</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e863216c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs41MS2bmUdJVHjibkLiaOtQ7MBvuvNWbrJichNBMn1z1op93CPqYp17Q3OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dweg4rzpz\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Transformer 和 MoE 在 decoder 块中有所不同：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Transformer 使用前馈网络。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">MoE 使用 experts，它们是前馈网络，但与 Transformer 中的网络相比更小。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在推理过程中，将选择专家的子集。这使得 MoE 中的推理速度更快。</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e62e84d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs4lR4xJa9NYBu89AgX1pCofaKd4QQdviawmlSiczhibDviaec5HlrH4miaf6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dqjq31q2g\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">由于网络包含多个解码器层：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">文本会在不同的层中经过不同的专家。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每个 token 选择的专家也各不相同。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是，模型如何决定哪些专家是理想的呢？</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这由路由器（Router）来完成。接下来我们来讨论它。</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11a8d122&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs4pURibianlAPhjKfBZDD6D0oIjUNLrCTGzgic9mfEM9ic6ZNnPOu6dNIicaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3D10gwdqfq\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">路由器就像一个多分类分类器，它对专家生成 softmax 分数。根据这些分数，我们选择前 K 个专家。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">路由器与网络一起训练，并学习如何选择最合适的专家。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但这并不简单。让我们来看看其中的挑战！</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36debc17&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs4mciaccvr0bU1fKKF2xcQpQOR30xAQJDIj1DAyBtmsYD3fUyalhdiccaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3D0fkkperc\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">挑战 1）注意训练初期的这一模式：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型选择“专家 2”</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">该专家变得稍微更好</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可能会再次被选中</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">该专家学到更多知识</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">又被选中</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学到更多知识</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如此循环！</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">许多专家因此训练不足！</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=129a532a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs4JE2HeuyVxBPvZe7GcVwA9eVLbhPkL1s9ZJ6tXPfhwDr3jrVnXJYSIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3D5socgofq\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们通过两个步骤来解决这个问题：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在路由器的前馈输出中添加噪声，使其他专家的 logits 更高。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n    <li>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">将除前 K 个之外的所有 logits 设为负无穷大，这样在 softmax 之后，这些分数就变为零。</span></span></p>\n     </div></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这样，其他专家也有机会参与训练。</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1c254349&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs46yDgtu3YK1Gtu5aicR8HlMJZIt8qV56INUJxJE2hVoaD9zbTwV6mafw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dh0xum7y3\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">挑战 2）某些专家可能会比其他专家处理更多的 token，导致部分专家训练不足。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们通过限制每个专家可处理的 token 数量来避免这种情况。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果某个专家达到上限，输入的 token 就会被传递给下一个最合适的专家。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">MoE 具有更多的参数需要加载，但由于每次仅选择部分专家，因此只有一部分参数被激活。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这使得推理速度更快。@MistralAI 的 Mixtral 8x7B 就是一个基于 MoE 的知名大型语言模型（LLM）。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"text-align: left;margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面是对比 Transformer 和 MoE 的示意图！</span></span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: block;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;width: 640px !important;height: 480px !important;\" data-w=\"640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3567c6f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F90bJEnAOK2GUY0d9icuAibbd0bAEMgvJs4PCYjt1Un9H6eC11ibLmB7sCWIGZNrGlwgUWcgFHzIGwib7HBczDFDrJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dzr3jivgy\"></span>\n    <figcaption>\n     <br>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "图解分析了 Transformer 与 MoE 架构的核心差异、工作原理及训练挑战，突出 MoE 在推理效率上的优势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "图解分析了 Transformer 与 MoE 架构的核心差异、工作原理及训练挑战，突出 MoE 在推理效率上的优势。",
  "summary": "文章以图解形式深入浅出地阐释了专家混合（MoE）架构如何改进传统 Transformer 模型。它首先对比了两种模型在解码器块中的区别，指出 MoE 通过引入更小的“专家”前馈网络实现模型优化。文章详细介绍了路由器（Router）机制如何动态选择最适合的专家，从而提高推理速度。随后，文章着重分析了 MoE 模型训练初期可能遇到的两大挑战：部分专家训练不足和 token 分配不均，并提供了相应的解决方案，如在路由器输出中添加噪声和限制每个专家处理的 token 数量。最后，文章强调 MoE 虽参数量大，但因仅激活部分专家，推理速度反而更快，并提及了 DeepSeek V3、R1 和 Mixtral 8x7B 等知名 MoE 模型。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MoE 通过引入专家前馈网络替代 Transformer 的 FFN，实现模型改进。",
      "explanation": "MoE 架构在解码器块中采用多个小型专家网络，而非单一大型前馈网络，允许模型根据输入选择性地激活部分专家，从而提升模型效率和性能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "路由器机制动态选择专家，显著提升 MoE 模型的推理速度。",
      "explanation": "路由器作为多分类分类器，根据 softmax 分数选择前 K 个最匹配的专家处理输入，确保每个 token 都能高效地被处理，从而加快整体推理过程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MoE 训练需解决专家训练不均和 token 分配挑战，以确保模型性能。",
      "explanation": "为避免部分专家过度训练和另一些专家训练不足，MoE 通过向路由器输出添加噪声和限制每个专家处理 token 数量的策略，促进专家间的均衡训练。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "专家混合（MoE）是一种流行的架构，比如最近火爆天的 DeepSeek V3 和 R1 就是这类模型。它利用不同的'专家'来改进 Transformer 模型。",
    "在推理过程中，将选择专家的子集。这使得 MoE 中的推理速度更快。",
    "路由器就像一个多分类分类器，它对专家生成 softmax 分数。根据这些分数，我们选择前 K 个专家。",
    "MoE 具有更多的参数需要加载，但由于每次仅选择部分专家，因此只有一部分参数被激活。这使得推理速度更快。"
  ],
